From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: gregordinary <33880035+gregordinary@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 01:26:51 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] rockchip: rk3576-generic: drop to the u-boot prompt by
 default

The maskrom console image is a bring-up tool driven over UART; autoboot
races the operator for the prompt, and the boot targets it would scan
for are exactly the code paths under debug. Disable autoboot
(bootdelay -1): the shell comes up immediately, and booting is an
explicit 'bootflow scan' away.

Signed-off-by: gregordinary <33880035+gregordinary@users.noreply.github.com>
---
 configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig b/configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig
index 3a6044b5..a3e4c991 100644
--- a/configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig
+++ b/configs/generic-rk3576_defconfig
@@ -9,6 +9,7 @@ CONFIG_SYS_LOAD_ADDR=0x40c00800
 CONFIG_DEBUG_UART_BASE=0x2AD40000
 CONFIG_DEBUG_UART_CLOCK=24000000
 CONFIG_DEBUG_UART=y
+CONFIG_BOOTDELAY=-1
 # CONFIG_BOOTMETH_VBE is not set
 CONFIG_DEFAULT_FDT_FILE="rockchip/rk3576-generic.dtb"
 # CONFIG_DISPLAY_CPUINFO is not set
